Power Input
===========

|Product| can be powered by 12V DC power supply. The power input connector is a 2-pin, 3.81mm screw terminal.

The **POWER** button can be used to switch the power ON or OFF.

The power input section of |product| features a range of protection features, including over-current, over-voltage, power surge, and reverse polarity protection, allowing it to meet stringent industrial safety regulations.

.. rst-class:: text-center

  |power_img|

  *12V DC Power Input*

.. note:: 
   
  If the product is used to control some key processes, it is highly recommended to use an Uninterruptible Power Supply (UPS) to prevent critical data loss.
  
:pagebreak:`True`

